overview.Name: Oracle Corporation
overview.Description: Oracle Corporation, based in Austin, Texas, is a leading global technology firm renowned for its comprehensive suite of enterprise software solutions and cloud computing services. As a frontrunner in cloud infrastructure, Oracle leverages cutting-edge technologies like artificial intelligence and machine learning to drive digital transformation across various industries, enhancing operational efficiencies for its extensive global clientele. The company's robust commitment to research and development empowers it to remain agile and innovative, effectively addressing the evolving demands of the competitive technology landscape.
overview.Address: 2300 ORACLE WAY, AUSTIN, TX, UNITED STATES, 78741
